---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Karen Arze | Home">
    <section style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 60px; margin-bottom: 80px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <div style="flex: 1.5; min-width: 300px;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 4rem; margin: 0; line-height: 1;">Karen Arze</h1>
            <p style="color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 3px; margin-bottom: 30px;">Optical Professional </p>
            <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; border-left: 2px solid var(--gold); padding-left: 20px;">
                Quick to adapt and eager to learn, I am reliable enough to take on leadership roles and always strive for work that can model what I would like to see in others. I'm always enthusiastic to apply my experiences into an environment that appreciates organization and efficiency!
            </p>
            <div style="margin-top: 40px; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> Norfolk, Virginia</p>
                <p><strong>Inquiries:</strong> 757-515-**** | karen_nat*@yahoo.com</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="flex: 1; text-align: center;">
            <div style="width: 350px; height: 450px; background: #ddd; border: 1px solid var(--gold); padding: 10px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <img src="/Arze_K/karen.jpg" alt="Karen Arze" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <h2 style="text-align: center; font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 40px;">Personal Interests</h2>
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 30px;">
        <div style="padding: 20px; background: white;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--gold);">The Shoreline</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Long walks on the beach. Even if it's a bit of a drive, it's always worth being able to see the beautiful sunrise!</p>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 20px; background: white;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--gold);">The Rhythm</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Dancing—Bachata, Meringue, Jazz, and Salsa. This is when I feel the most like myself!</p>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 20px; background: white;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--gold);">The Kitchen</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Experimental cooking. Challenging myself with available ingredients to create family favorites.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 20px; border: 2px solid var(--gold); text-align: center;">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">My Heart ❤️</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">My Son and Daughter are my pride and joy! Though they're grown, they will always be my babies.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</MainLayout>
